Characters : In characters marked with an asterisk (*; viz., 6, 10, 12, 13, 18, 20, 31, 39, 42 ), fit and steps are not given as the character is not significant to the analysis but was kept here to indicate an autapomorphy for a terminal taxon. (0) Eye tubercle in males and females: (0) low (
